                            </p>
                            <button class="button">See More</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card swiper-slide">
                        <div class="image-content">
                            <span class="overlay">

                            </span>
                            <div class="card-image">
                                <img src="~/images/New_Images/2.jpg" alt="" class="card-img">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <h2 class="name">24/04/2023</h2>
                            <p class="description">
                                MUA VÉ NHANH HƠN BAO GIỜ HẾT VỚI APP NCC
                            </p>
